## curl (manual testing / scripting)

```bash
# Insert
curl -X POST "$OPENSAIL_DATA_API_URL/submissions" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $OPENSAIL_DATA_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"email":"a@b.com","message":"hi"}'

# List
curl "$OPENSAIL_DATA_API_URL/submissions?limit=20" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $OPENSAIL_DATA_KEY"

# Get / update / delete
curl "$OPENSAIL_DATA_API_URL/submissions/$ID" -H "Authorization: Bearer $OPENSAIL_DATA_KEY"
curl -X PATCH "$OPENSAIL_DATA_API_URL/submissions/$ID" -H "Authorization: Bearer $OPENSAIL_DATA_KEY" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"...":"..."}'
curl -X DELETE "$OPENSAIL_DATA_API_URL/submissions/$ID" -H "Authorization: Bearer $OPENSAIL_DATA_KEY"
```

